# `infrastructure/`

**I/O allowed:** SQLite, Gemini, disk, network, third-party SDKs.

## Imports

**Allowed:** `orchestrator_v4.core.ports`, `orchestrator_v4.core.entities`, drivers and stdlib.

**Forbidden:** `orchestrator_v4.presentation`.

**Avoid:** importing `orchestrator_v4.core.use_cases`—adapters implement **ports**, not use-case modules.

## Adapters

- One adapter (or a small related set) per port contract.
- Keep storage and HTTP details out of `core/`.

## Naming

- Name both tech and role, e.g. `SqliteInterviewSessionTurnStore`—not bare `Gateway` / `Repository`.
